comments: Porter Jr. (DEN) makes contact to Beal's (WAS) shoulder that affects his driving shot attempt.
Lopez (WAS) maintains a legal guarding position during Jokic's (DEN) driving shot attempt.
Correctly called backcourt violation on WAS.
Murray (DEN) makes contact with the ball and he dislodges it from Westbrook (WAS).
Beal (WAS) legally re-establishes position in bounds before making contact with the ball.
Jokic (DEN) swipes down and makes clean contact with the ball during Lopez's (WAS) shot attempt near the rim.
Murray (DEN) places his off-arm against Neto (WAS) with slight extension as he releases and Neto's momentum carries him away from the marginal contact.  The contact occurs at the 00:38.8 mark.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a legal position in Neto's (WAS) path and he absorbs the oncoming contact during the pick.
Hachimura (WAS) legally contests Murray's (DEN) jump shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Jokic (DEN) makes marginal contact to Neto's (WAS) off-arm after he releases the ball during his driving shot attempt.
Neto (WAS) makes marginal contact to Campazzo's (DEN) arm after he releases the ball during his jump shot attempt.
